      "id": "33564953eb18182f784777591249d29fa9c53313",
      "message": "Improvements to `Context.Output` use (#14930)\n\n- Add `check_enabled` to `Context` and use that instead of `if_enabled`.\n- Return errors in a few places to lower nesting.\n- Remove `if_fetch_method` and `if_post_method` and replace with simpler `is_fetch_method` and `is_post_method`.\n- Add `write_operation` flag to `Data.post` and `AWS.signed_post` (default as a write operation).\n<img width=\"513\" height=\"284\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/4da50a4c-a19f-45ed-bd7c-36cbf77f1ed3\" />\n<img width=\"908\" height=\"62\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/cae7cdfb-9cbe-483c-87b3-be934b537828\" />\n- Add `write_operation` flag to `Process.run` (default as a non-write operation).\n<img width=\"676\" height=\"88\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/e87c031c-32d7-4a77-84d4-9c709d0417c3\" />",
      "timestamp": "2026-03-31T18:12:30Z",
